  "html": "<u>Intro 2x: <i>C#m</i>  <i>E</i>  <i>B</i>\r\n</u><u>Riff 1:\r\n</u><b>E|-------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>B|-------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>G|----------------------------6--------|   (2x)\r\n</b><b>D|------------4-2----------------------|\r\n</b><b>A|2-4-2-4-2-4-----2-4-2-4-2-4----------|\r\n</b><b>E|-------------------------------------|\r\n\r\n</b><u>Riff 2:\r\n</u><b>E|--------------------------------|------------------------------------||\r\n</b><b>B|------------9----9-7----9-7-----|-------------9-----9-7-----9-7------||\r\n</b><b>G|4-4/6-6-8-9--4-4----4-4-----4-4-|-6-4-6-6-8-9---4-4-----4-4-----4-4--||\r\n</b><b>D|--------------------------------|------------------------------------||\r\n</b><b>A|--------------------------------|------------------------------------||\r\n</b><b>E|--------------------------------|------------------------------------||\r\n\r\n</b><u> <i>C#</i>            <i>A</i>       <i>C#</i>        <i>A</i>\r\n</u><u>Descerá sobre mim, a unção do Senhor\r\n</u><u>          <i>E</i>        <i>B/D#</i>    <i>C#m</i>       <i>F#9</i>\r\n</u><u>Sinto em mim fogo consumidor, já arder.\r\n</u><u>      <i>C#</i>          <i>A</i>          <i>C#</i>          <i>A</i>\r\n</u><u>Vou pedir, vou buscar, vou sonhar, conquistar\r\n</u><u>     <i>E</i>          <i>B/D#</i>      <i>C#m</i>           <i>B</i>\r\n</u><u>Derramar minha vida no altar, e te adorar.\r\n\r\n</u><u>       <i>E</i>                        <i>A</i>        <i>G#m</i>\r\n</u><u>Vou correr, para Deus, como um rio corre para o mar\r\n</u><u>   <i>F#m</i>        <i>B</i>\r\n</u><u>Eu corro para Ti.\r\n</u><u>       <i>E</i>                      <i>A</i>            <i>G#m</i>\r\n</u><u>Vou viver, só pra Deus, regressar ao meu lugar\r\n</u><u>         <i>F#m</i>           <i>B</i>\r\n</u><u>E ao primeiro amor voltar.\r\n\r\n</u><u> Solo: <i>C#m</i>  <i>E</i>  <i>B</i>\r\n</u><b>E|-7-5-4-----4-0---2---7------------------|\r\n</b><b>B|-------5-------2